हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/7dm5vF
show.description: Ishita Malhotra, a wealthy heiress, hides her true identity to find love and purpose on her own terms. But when her trust is shattered by a double betrayal Jay Mehta’s deceit and Rhea’s ruthless schemes her world unravels.Out of heartbreak and humiliation, Ishita rises stronger, wiser, and ready to reclaim what’s hers. With each shocking revelation, she fights to restore her name, dignity, and the love she truly deserves.A tale of masked identities, betrayal, and fierce redemption where the crown isn’t given, it’s earned.
